Package com.example.Hotel

Class Manager

java.lang.Object
com.example.Hotel.Person
com.example.Hotel.Manager
public class Manager extends Person
Represents a manager within a hotel, including their start date and years of experience. The Manager class inherits from the Person class.
Author:
Ferran Calabuig Herrero
